    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level example of the E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with its signature 8,000 RPM redline. This vehicle is mechanically superlative; the VANOS system has been fully overhauled with Beisan components, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. The individual throttle bodies are perfectly synchronized, providing the sharp, linear throttle response that defines this chassis. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox retains its factory-tight shift pattern, paired with a limited-slip differential that exhibits no chatter. Riding on a refreshed suspension with OEM-spec dampers and bushings, the handling remains precise and communicative. The exterior retains its original factory luster with zero paint correction required, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean, showing no signs of oxidation or fluid seepage. This is a blue-chip investment for the discerning collector who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
