    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "Presented in absolute showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of care and preservation. Always stored in a climate-controlled garage, the exterior paint maintains a deep, mirror-like luster free of any rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather remains supple and factory-fresh, while every button and electronic system functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, having been maintained strictly by certified specialists with a folder of comprehensive service records included. For the buyer seeking a collector-grade example that drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership, this is an unparalleled opportunity.",
